OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally spoke to
OL,8,FAshleigh Eccles, who was diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith breast cancer 12 days after
OL,10,Fgiving birth
OL,12,FA mum is backing a campaign hoping to
OL,13,Flevel the playing field for new
OL,14,Fmothers diagnosed with cancer - with
OL,15,Fmany forced to use up their maternity
OL,16,Fleave to get treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
