FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FThe campaign, by charity Mummy's Star,
OL,7,Fsays while fathers are able to defer
OL,8,Ftheir leave for up to 52 weeks the
OL,9,Fsame rules do not apply to mums,
OL,10,Fleaving them with little or no time
OL,11,Fleft to bond with their new baby.
OL,13,FAshleigh Eccles was diagnosed with
OL,14,Fbreast cancer just 12 days after
OL,15,Fgiving birth.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FAfter struggling to breast feed the
OL,7,Fmum from Cheshire went to a lactation
OL,8,Fconsultation, where, "sitting with a
OL,9,Fnewborn baby in our arms we got
OL,10,Ftold... it was very, very likely that
OL,11,Fwe were looking at a breast cancer
OL,12,Fdiagnosis."
OL,14,FAs a result Ashleigh's whole maternity
OL,15,Fleave was taken up with cancer
OL,16,Ftreatment.
OL,18,F"There were real moments of absolute
OL,19,Fheartbreak within my maternity leave,
OL,20,For so-called maternity leave,"
OL,21,FAshleigh said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,F"I couldn't do the things that other
OL,7,Fpeople do during maternity leave. I
OL,8,Fcouldn't breastfeed, some days I
OL,9,Fcouldn't get out of bed.
OL,11,F"I had to have my husband bring my
OL,12,Fbaby to me and he had to hold her
OL,13,Fagainst my chest because it was
OL,14,Fimpossible for me to actually hold her.
OL,16,F"I had excruciating pain and I wasn't
OL,17,Fgetting any sleep."
OL,19,FAs well as losing the time with her
OL,20,Fdaughter, who is now three, she was
OL,21,Falso told she would lose her fertility.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FAshleigh was offered the opportunity
OL,7,Fto freeze her eggs but it would take
OL,8,Feight weeks to do so, and she was told
OL,9,Fshe should begin treatment as soon as
OL,10,Fpossible as her cancer was aggressive.
OL,12,FShe said: "It helped that you had a
OL,13,Fbeautiful newborn in your arms, that
OL,14,Fyou could just focus on getting well
OL,15,Ffor them because to be honest, at that
OL,16,Fpoint you're fighting for your life
OL,17,Fand you're fighting for your baby."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FEvery day, at least two women in the
OL,7,FUK are diagnosed with cancer during
OL,8,Fpregnancy or within the first year
OL,9,Fafter giving birth, meaning hundreds
OL,10,Fof new mothers face losing much - or
OL,11,Fall - of their maternity leave while
OL,12,Fundergoing treatment.
OL,14,FAshleigh said if she had been given
OL,15,Fthe choice to pause her maternity
OL,16,Fleave, "I would have had hope during
OL,17,Fthat time that I wasn't doing any
OL,18,Fdamage to the bond that I had with my
OL,19,Fdaughter."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,F"I would have known that at the end of
OL,7,Fall this, I have got that time
OL,8,Fprotected," she added.
OL,10,F"I can do all these lovely things that
OL,11,Fmake you feel like you'd been a good
OL,12,Fmother.
OL,14,F"And I would hope that any women in
OL,15,Fthe future with a similar diagnosis
OL,16,Fwould have a bit of hope during those
OL,17,Freally dark times."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
