OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FGlossop-based charity Mummy's Star is
OL,7,Fnow campaigning for new mothers who
OL,8,Fhave been diagnosed with cancer to be
OL,9,Fable to defer their maternity leave
OL,10,Funtil after their treatment.
OL,12,FPete Wallroth started the charity in
OL,13,F2013 after his wife Mair died from
OL,14,Fbreast cancer 10 weeks after the birth
OL,15,Fof their son Merlin.
OL,17,FHe says he launched the charity when
OL,18,Fhe realised there was a gap in support
OL,19,Ffor families balancing pregnancy or a
OL,20,Fnewborn baby with cancer treatment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,F"We set up Mummy's Star to try and
OL,7,Fensure that all the families diagnosed
OL,8,Fin similar kind of circumstances to us
OL,9,Fdidn't feel as isolated and alone," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"Managing the simple things that we
OL,13,Fshould enjoy as parents, like being
OL,14,Fable to feed a baby, being able to put
OL,15,Fthem down, and rock them to sleep.
OL,17,F"All of a sudden those things become
OL,18,Freally physically difficult because of
OL,19,Fthe crippling fatigue."
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FPete says Mummy's Star have supported
OL,7,Fother families who have had to be
OL,8,Fquarantined from their newborn after
OL,9,Fgoing through radioactive cancer
OL,10,Ftherapies, or cannot be near them due
OL,11,Fto life saving operations which is
OL,12,Fheartbreaking.
OL,14,F"If I had fallen sick during my
OL,15,Fpaternity leave, I could have paused
OL,16,Fit and then recommenced it when I felt
OL,17,Fbetter," Pete added.
OL,19,F"It is cruel in the extreme that a
OL,20,Fsick parent who's just given birth
OL,21,Fcannot have the same opportunity."
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FHe said that the change would bring
OL,7,Fmaternity leave in line with current
OL,8,Fpaternity leave regulations, helping
OL,9,Femployers support their staff as they
OL,10,Fwant to too.
OL,12,F"It is hopefully that simple, and it
OL,13,Fgives everybody the clarity that they
OL,14,Fneed rather than this no man's land,
OL,15,Fwhich is what families and employers
OL,16,Fsadly find themselves in an awful lot
OL,17,Fat the moment," he said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FAshleigh did not return to work after
OL,7,Fher treatment because she did not have
OL,8,Fthe time to get back her sense of self
OL,9,Fbefore she would have had to go back.
OL,11,FShe loved the company, having worked
OL,12,Fthere for 21 years.
OL,14,F"It was an identity losing time," she
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"Becoming a mum you put on a different
OL,18,Fhat. But becoming a mum who was also a
OL,19,Fcancer patient, the identity was
OL,20,Ftotally gone the person that I was
OL,21,Fbefore.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,F"If I'd have had the time to also
OL,7,Fbuild myself back up... then I think
OL,8,Fthat I most definitely would have
OL,9,Ffound the time to return to work."
OL,11,FAshleigh added: "I hope that for women
OL,12,Fin the future, it's not something that
OL,13,Fthey have to even have to consider.
OL,15,F"That they can just focus on
OL,16,Fthemselves, on their baby, and take
OL,17,Fthe time to recover and return back to
OL,18,Fthe workplace when they feel ready to
OL,19,Fdo so."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,FIn 2024, Ireland passed legislation
OL,7,Fallowing mums to defer maternity leave
OL,8,Fduring cancer treatment, following
OL,9,Fcampaigning from the Irish Cancer
OL,10,FSociety.
OL,12,FThey are the first country to do so,
OL,13,Fand now High Peak's MP John Pearce is
OL,14,Fhoping the UK will follow suit.
OL,16,F"Hearing stories of women who are
OL,17,Fspending most of their maternity leave
OL,18,Fgetting treatment and then going back
OL,19,Fto work feeling that they've not
OL,20,Fbonded with their babies," The Labour
OL,21,FMP said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1775585464
OL,3,C'You're fighting for your life': Mums
OL,4,Cwith cancer lose out on maternity leave
OL,6,F"It's truly tragic and I think there's
OL,7,Fmore that we can do in this space to
OL,8,Fsupport these families."
OL,10,FMr Pearce is encouraging the 700
OL,11,Ffamilies a year affected by this issue
OL,12,Fto come forward and share their
OL,13,Fexperiences.
OL,15,FThe government is currently carrying
OL,16,Fout a review and say it is committed
OL,17,Fto improve the parental system for
OL,18,Feveryone, employees and businesses.
OL,26,@pD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
